               <msContents>
                  <summary>Psalter, ዳዊት፡, Introduction of Gə‘əz Grammar, Säwasäw, ሰዋስወ፡ ግእዝ፡</summary>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from = "1r" to = "162v"/><title type = "complete" ref="LIT2701Dawit"/>
                     <note>
                    ‎<locus from="1r" to="130v"/> Psalms of David;
                    <locus from="130v" to="141v"/> Biblical Canticles;
                    <locus from="142r" to="147v"/> Song of Songs, common version;
                    <locus from="147v" to="144r"/> Praises of Mary, Wəddase Maryam, ውዳሴ፡ ማርያም፡, ‎arranged for the days of the week (Monday, <locus target="#147v"/>; Tuesday, <locus target="#‎‎148v"/>; Wednesday, <locus target="#150r"/>; Thursday, <locus target="#152r"/>; Friday, <locus target="#154r"/>; ‎Saturday, <locus target="#155r"/>; Sunday, <locus target="#156v"/>), (incomplete at the end);
                    <locus from="157r" to="161r"/> Gate of Light [Anqäsä Bərhan], exclusive of <locus target="#159r #159v #160r #‎‎160v"/>, (incomplete at the beginning)‎
                  </note>
                  </msItem>
               <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from = "161r" to = "162v"/>
                  <title>Introduction of Gǝ‘ǝz Grammar, Säwasäw, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሰዋስወ፡ ግእዝ፡</foreign> (incomplete ‎at the end)‎</title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                    ‎ሰዋስው፡ ብ፡ መሸጋገሪያ፡ ወዓዲ፡ መሰላል፡ ሰዋስው፡ ርኢኩ፡ መሰላልን፡ አየሁ፡ ‎‎ሰዋስው፡ ሐሰስኩ፡ መሰላልን፡ ሻሁ፡ ሰዋስው፡ ረከብኩ፡ (inserted) መሰላልን፡ ‎‎አገኝሁ፡ ሰዋስው፡ ቀበጽኩ፡ መሰላልን፡ አጣሁ፡ ሰዋስው፡ ገሰስኩ፡ መሰላልን፡ ዳሰስሁ፡...‎
                  </incipit>
                </msItem>
